  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They-- they're liberals.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Even now in Saudi Arabia, some poor guy steals-- steals something, a tire or a jacket, he gets his hand cut off, or the second time he gets his foot cut off.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But the-- but the-- the-- the so-called sheikhs, the so-called the princes and kings, they are-- are able to steal anywhere from $1 million to $10 billion.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And the money that-- from the oils, which God gave to all the Arabs, he didn't give it just to a few Arabs, to the Arab sheiks who are strong enough to have an army to suppress the others.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And that's why we saw that-- that bombing in-- in-- in Saudi Arabia a few weeks ago.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And as sure as I'm sitting here talking to you, as sure as that, I'm sure that in the next few years those princes will be overthrown, and they will all be killed, even if they run to America.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "They already have billions of dollars stashed away in America, and Britain, France, and in-- in Japan, and all over the world, billions of dollars.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Airplanes on the ready to take off, but they-- all of them, and they're deliberately paying money to-- to terrorist organizations to attack the Jews.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And they even pay money in the Philippines to the Muslims there.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Because they want the focus to be on others.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "They want all these organizations to focus on other people, not on them.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Because the biggest criminals, the ones who have done the Arabs the most harm, are these sheikhs, these Arab princes and royal-- self-styled royalty errand boy royalties, who are stealing what belongs to the Arab people.",
      "word_count": 36
    }
  ],
